    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/18/125391187/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_1695795997484997695.png",
                "key": "弦月舞步",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "弦月舞步"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，如果隊伍中包含<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素角色</span>和<span style=\"color: #99FF88\">草元素角色</span>且不包含其他元素的角色，就生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">金杯的豐饋</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">金杯的豐饋</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">敵方角色受到綻放反應時：</span>我方不再生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">草原核</span>，而是改為召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">豐穰之核</span>。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/18/125391187/c82a120ef3389c55999b6069de0c8ddc_7319834127739720049.png",
                "key": "七域舞步",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "七域舞步"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，目標角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">永世流沔</span>。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/18/125391187/e701a5d9dee57abe1f108242af52b000_4077622828884466030.png",
                "key": "浮蓮舞步‧遠夢聆泉",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "浮蓮舞步‧遠夢聆泉"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1</span>（可疊加，最多疊加到3次）</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方宣布結束時：</span>如果此牌的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>至少為2，則造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>。（需消耗<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>）</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/18/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8229536494062796561.png",
                "key": "豐穰之核",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/18/125391187/ded0956520d3dce12af6dfcbdfab5d01_1003445197228285975.png",
                "title": "豐穰之核"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/18/125391187/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_8338008289218099773.png",
                "key": "水元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/18/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_844425251767480373.png",
